Class Permission

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.azure.documentdb.Resource
      • com.microsoft.azure.documentdb.Permission

  • public class Permission
extends Resource
    Represents a per-User Permission to access a specific resource e.g. Document or Collection
